snippet.title: Official Doritos Crash Course Trailer
snippet.description:
Doritos Crash Course will be released on December 9th, 2010. Download the game for free and vote for ILL JILL if you like the game! 

http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/Doritos-Crash-Course-Voting-Pic/00000000-0000-4002-802f-000558570887

Visit unlockxbox.com, outofgames.net, or join the facebook page at facebook.com/doritoscrashcourse for more info!
